            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Once</strong> the onion is soft, add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tbsp)</span> of sugar, the red wine vinegar, the Henderson's relish and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(4 tbsp)</span> of water</p>\r\n<p><strong>Turn</strong> the heat down to the lowest setting and simmer the onions gently for a further 10-15min, or until they're sticky and most of the water is absorbed</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
